Seems like `getEvaluatingGroup` is raising some errors. I have read the doc [here](https://github.com/jiahanxie353/circt/blob/14e0ca0227ed33c56d6d8b65ea42bcdd54991613/include/circt/Dialect/Calyx/CalyxLoweringUtils.h#L429)  but I'm still not entirely sure what it does. Which phase is it used in? Build-component/group-phase, or build-control-phase?
